      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's a common feeling when the excitement of a dream fades against the reality of endless walking; the beauty of Prague is often in the moments you didn't plan, not just the monuments on your list. You might consider taking a break and letting yourself just wander without a destination to rediscover that sense of wonder. Perhaps the most important \"stop\" was simply sitting here and observing the city's rhythm for two hours, which already proves you found something meaningful.",
