      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont think wandering is gonna help though. it's not about being tired or needing a break. it's more like... i've reached the end of the map. i've checked out all the boxes and everything is just grayscale now. once you've reached the final landmark, there's nowhere else to go but out, you know? like the journey is just over.",
